    "15": {
      "answer": "Relational contracts refer to informal agreements based on trust, mutual understanding, and long-term cooperation rather than strict legal enforcement. In long-term partnerships, they help reduce uncertainty, improve flexibility, and encourage collaboration. Instead of specifying every detail, partners rely on shared norms and trust, which lowers transaction costs and makes it easier to adapt to changes.",
